"A.P.241/10/15 11:00": "Phew, was it just me or... Did the enemies feel really strong today..."
"Hehehe. That is probably, very likely, the answer and not just your imagination."
"Yes, it's Lisa, hello! This must have been quite the mission if it required two Guardians on a sortie together."

"Oh, we were on the Bridge together, so...
But never mind that. You said it wasn't just my imagination?"
"About the enemies, that is. They were, to sum it up in one word, tough. In two words, strong and tough."
"Lisa would know these things, since she shoots and shoots and shoots all kinds of Darkers."
"These ones that that just appeared were different. They were stronger, and tougher, and stranger."
"Also, also, the alarms were too slow to respond to an invasion of this extent."
"What are the chances that, now of all times, nobody was able to predict this attack?"
"Lisa only knows what happened. The enemy's strength was unusual, and our response was unusual too. That's all Lisa knows."
"Well, Lisa is off to find more of those strangely powerful Darkers to play with. Ehehe, hehehehehe."
"<%me>, Matoi, the situation seems to be all clear now. Could you please return to the Bridge?"
